OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Faffecting eastern areas, perhaps heavy
OL,7,Fat first, before easing away
OL,8,Fsouthwards by around midnight. Low
OL,9,Fcloud, mist and some light rain and
OL,10,Fdrizzle then spreading from the
OL,11,Fnortheast. Less cold than recent
OL,12,Fnights.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FCloudy with light rain for
OL,15,Fsome, although turning mainly dry for
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Cooler than recently,
OL,17,Fespecially in the northeasterly
OL,18,Fbreeze. Turning brighter with some
OL,19,Fsunshine later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
